OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSpending power squeeze     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworst for 20 years         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Regular pay is falling at the fastest  
OL,6, rate since 2001 when taking into       
OL,7, account rising prices, the Office for  
OL,8, National Statistics has said.          
OL,10,FBetween March and May, pay excluding   
OL,11,Fbonuses was down 2.8% from a year      
OL,12,Fearlier when adjusted for inflation -  
OL,13,Fthe fastest drop since records began.  
OL,15,FHousehold budgets are being hit by     
OL,16,Fsoaring food, fuel and energy costs,   
OL,17,Fwith inflation at a 40-year high.      
OL,19,FMeanwhile, job vacancies continued to  
OL,20,Fincrease, although the rate is slowing.
